{"members":[{"header_text":" في قوله تعالى:","body_text":" <quranic_text>«وَ لِكُلِّ قَوْمٍ هٰادٍ»</quranic_text> <footnote>[الرعد۷]</footnote> ، وَ اَنَّ النَّبِيَّ صَلَّي اللَّهُ عَلَيْهِ وَ الِهِ وَ سَلَّمَ قَالَ: اَنْتَ الْهَادِي يَا عَلِيُّ بِكَ يَهْتَدِي الْمُهْتَدُونَ مِنْ بَعْدِي.","translation":"","aligned_body":"TAG_OPEN:quranic_text وَ لِكُلِّ قَوْمٍ هٰادٍ TAG_CLOSE:quranic_text TAG_OPEN:footnote الرعد ۷ TAG_CLOSE:footnote وَ اَنَّ النَّبِيَّ صَلَّي اللَّهُ عَلَيْهِ وَ الِهِ وَ سَلَّمَ قَالَ اَنْتَ الْهَادِي يَا عَلِيُّ بِكَ يَهْتَدِي الْمُهْتَدُونَ مِنْ بَعْدِي"}],"body_consensus_columns":[{"kind":"tag_open","tag_name":"quranic_text"},{"kind":"word","token":"و","display":"وَ"},{"kind":"word","token":"لكل","display":"لِكُلِّ"},{"kind":"word","token":"قوم","display":"قَوْمٍ"},{"kind":"word","token":"هاد","display":"هٰادٍ"},{"kind":"tag_close","tag_name":"quranic_text"},{"kind":"tag_open","tag_name":"footnote"},{"kind":"word","token":"الرعد","display":"الرعد"},{"kind":"word","token":"۷","display":"۷"},{"kind":"tag_close","tag_name":"footnote"},{"kind":"word","token":"و","display":"وَ"},{"kind":"word","token":"ان","display":"اَنَّ"},{"kind":"word","token":"النبي","display":"النَّبِيَّ"},{"kind":"word","token":"صلي","display":"صَلَّي"},{"kind":"word","token":"الله","display":"اللَّهُ"},{"kind":"word","token":"عليه","display":"عَلَيْهِ"},{"kind":"word","token":"و","display":"وَ"},{"kind":"word","token":"اله","display":"الِهِ"},{"kind":"word","token":"و","display":"وَ"},{"kind":"word","token":"سلم","display":"سَلَّمَ"},{"kind":"word","token":"قال","display":"قَالَ"},{"kind":"word","token":"انت","display":"اَنْتَ"},{"kind":"word","token":"الهادي","display":"الْهَادِي"},{"kind":"word","token":"يا","display":"يَا"},{"kind":"word","token":"علي","display":"عَلِيُّ"},{"kind":"word","token":"بك","display":"بِكَ"},{"kind":"word","token":"يهتدي","display":"يَهْتَدِي"},{"kind":"word","token":"المهتدون","display":"الْمُهْتَدُونَ"},{"kind":"word","token":"من","display":"مِ